trans-unit.source: (string)URL for the default image or a default type. Accepts '404', 'retro', 'monsterid', 'wavatar', 'indenticon', 'mystery', 'mm', 'mysteryman', 'blank', or 'gravatar_default'. Default is the value of the 'avatar_default' option, with a fallback of 'mystery'.
